{"prompt": "Generate a website for a edtech platform. The website should be lively and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EdTech Platform</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #e53935; /* Red brand color */\n            color: white;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: white;\n            color: #e53935;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #f06262; /* Lighter red on hover */\n            color: white;\n        }\n        .features {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: white;\n        }\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #e53935;\n        }\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: #fefefe;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: #e53935;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #e53935;\n        }\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .testimonials {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n        }\n        .testimonials h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #e53935;\n        }\n        .testimonial-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .testimonial-item {\n            background-color: white;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            font-style: italic;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .testimonial-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .testimonial-item .author {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #e53935;\n            font-style: normal;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Animations */\n        @keyframes fadeInUp {\n            from {\n                opacity: 0;\n                transform: translateY(20px);\n            }\n            to {\n                opacity: 1;\n                transform: translateY(0);\n            }\n        }\n\n        .animate-on-scroll {\n            opacity: 0;\n            animation-fill-mode: forwards;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1, .hero p, .cta-button {\n            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;\n            animation-delay: 0.2s;\n        }\n\n        .features h2, .feature-item {\n            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;\n            animation-delay: 0.3s;\n        }\n\n        .testimonials h2, .testimonial-item {\n            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;\n            animation-delay: 0.4s;\n        }\n        \n        /* Simple responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.8em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n            .features h2, .testimonials h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Unlock Your Potential with Our EdTech Platform</h1>\n        <p>Engaging courses, innovative tools, and expert guidance to shape your future.</p>\n        <a href=\"#courses\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Courses</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"features\" id=\"features\">\n        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item animate-on-scroll\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chalkboard-teacher\"></i>\n                <h3>Expert Instructors</h3>\n                <p>Learn from industry leaders and seasoned educators passionate about sharing their knowledge.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item animate-on-scroll\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                <h3>Innovative Learning</h3>\n                <p>Experience interactive lessons, real-world projects, and cutting-edge technology.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item animate-on-scroll\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                <h3>Community Support</h3>\n                <p>Connect with a vibrant community of learners and find collaborative opportunities.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item animate-on-scroll\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                <h3>Career Advancement</h3>\n                <p>Gain skills that matter and open doors to new career paths and opportunities.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"testimonials\" id=\"testimonials\">\n        <h2>What Our Learners Say</h2>\n        <div class=\"testimonial-grid\">\n            <div class=\"testimonial-item animate-on-scroll\">\n                <p>\"This platform transformed my learning experience! The courses are so engaging and the instructors are top-notch.\"</p>\n                <div class=\"author\">- Sarah K.</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-item animate-on-scroll\">\n                <p>\"I landed my dream job after completing a course here. The practical skills I gained were invaluable.\"</p>\n                <div class=\"author\">- David L.</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-item animate-on-scroll\">\n                <p>\"The community is amazing! I've learned so much from my peers and made lasting connections.\"</p>\n                <div class=\"author\">- Maria P.</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"features\" id=\"courses\">\n        <h2>Our Popular Courses</h2>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item animate-on-scroll\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-code\"></i>\n                <h3>Web Development</h3>\n                <p>Master front-end and back-end technologies to build dynamic websites and applications.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item animate-on-scroll\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chart-pie\"></i>\n                <h3>Data Science</h3>\n                <p>Learn to analyze data, build predictive models, and extract insights.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item animate-on-scroll\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-robot\"></i>\n                <h3>Artificial Intelligence</h3>\n                <p>Explore the fundamentals of AI and machine learning to build intelligent systems.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item animate-on-scroll\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-dollar-sign\"></i>\n                <h3>Digital Marketing</h3>\n                <p>Learn strategies for SEO, social media, content creation, and campaign management.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    \n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 EdTech Platform. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n            const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n                entries.forEach(entry => {\n                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                        entry.target.style.animationPlayState = 'running';\n                    }\n                });\n            }, { threshold: 0.1 });\n\n            document.querySelectorAll('.animate-on-scroll').forEach(element => {\n                observer.observe(element);\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}